{"tid":2102034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［曲到圓］我呼籲大家千其要去書展！！！","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:02:50.000Z","uid":164491,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84830e7276cf0aff555790bd00cd085779681e63","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"原因好簡單<br />\n<br />\n１。書展室內多通風<strong>幾順暢</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乾淨既空氣經過通風系統話咁快飄到其他層都係<br />\n<br />\n２。相信個Ｄ以為搞唔成既書展商見到咁多人　一定喜極而泣<br />\n又可以<strong>一路數錢一路賣Ｄ貴撚到仆街既書　</strong><br />\n<br />\n３。經貿局&quot;見到呢個咁撚多人咁歡樂既畫面<br />\n又可以大肆宣揚國安法 對穩定社會幾咁成功 <br />\n今次仲唔俾佢賴到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3。引證番世衛幾個月之前既講法<br />\n武肺係唔會經空氣傳染 帶口罩都係無撚用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲各位怕悶既藍絲港豬出去一齊逼　一齊振興經濟！<br />\n順便除埋口罩　行完企起個ＨＡＬＬ度大家困獸鬥食番個好西先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n沒事兒～沒事兒～<br />\n相信政府<br />\n不怕兒～不怕兒～<br />\n一定要去！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd4511ffbf10842c66a51951fb13261ac090ce6","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"打錯左　要奶個個係貿發局先岩呀～"},{"pid":"8190d06cd484c3b83634bc811d63c644ac918b26","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<em><strong><strong><em>有冇人知入面有幾多中資既書商呀～</em></strong></strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d81efd3973cb605b7e1bc0821c8581a7391a7272","tid":2102034,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8190d06cd484c3b83634bc811d63c644ac918b26","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<em><strong><strong><em>有冇人知入面有幾多中資既書商呀～</em></strong></strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"ㄧ個中 冚包散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c1885696a4069575ed620e1dc6c8effe0d24bf","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81efd3973cb605b7e1bc0821c8581a7391a7272","tid":2102034,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8190d06cd484c3b83634bc811d63c644ac918b26","tid":2102034,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<em><strong><strong><em>有冇人知入面有幾多中資既書商呀～</em></strong></strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"ㄧ個中 冚包散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit